	</h2>

	
	
	<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
	
		<div class="post-date">		
			<p class="post-month">Aug</p>
			<p class="post-day">28</p>
			<p class="post-year">2002</p>				
		</div>

		The RIAA Website was hacked last night (via &#8220;Scripting News&#8221;). This was a pretty boneheaded move by whomever pulled it off. The content industries want to portray themselves as the responsible parties, and the other side of the debate as criminals and cynical, greedy tech companies. The responsible people in Hollywood and the record industry distinguish between the pirates and the people who just want to enjoy their music and ...
		
